description._content: Description: The geologist with plane table and telescopic alidade making a geological and topographical map. Description: A geologist at work in the field. Taken at Chashm Farak, near Tembium. Mr. G. M. Shaw in camp. Location: Chashm Farak, Tembiun, Persia Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/714 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives. Feel free to share it within the spirit of the Commons Please use the comments section below the pictures to share any information you have about the people, places or events shown. We have attempted to provide place information for the images automatically but our software may not have found the correct location.
